شركة السندس لخدمات التوظيف والإدارة
-
Abu Dhabi
1. Develop a framework for identifying, measuring, monitoring and evaluating strategic, financial and operational risks.
2. Manage the process of identifying and assessing the risks affecting the business
3. Develop and prepare risk policies to formalize the Company’s commitment to risk management and ensure compliance with applicable policies and regulations.
4. Maintain the corporate risk register to identify, analyze and manage risk.
5. Manage the procurement process for all insurance and all ongoing related matters, as required.
6. Participate in all aspects of the business to ensure the early identification of risk issues.
7. Develop a rolling schedule of risk workshops and reviews with all Project teams, including Project Managers and Consultants.
8. Drive the enterprise risk management strategy across the Company, engaging with all aspects of the business.
